511
00:33:53,680 --> 00:33:54,980
 I to moramo slijediti.

512
00:33:54,980 --> 00:33:56,800
 To je ono jedino što možemo.

513
00:33:57,240 --> 00:33:59,080
 Ali to postiće je stvarno

514
00:33:59,080 --> 00:33:59,920
 jako, jako teško.

515
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:01,280
 I onda se uvijek pitam,

516
00:34:01,280 --> 00:34:03,720
 da recimo preispitam

517
00:34:03,720 --> 00:34:04,400
 svoju ljubav,

518
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:07,000
 da li je to ona sebična ljubav,

519
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:08,520
 znači da ja volim

520
00:34:08,520 --> 00:34:09,460
 kad i mene netko voli,

521
00:34:09,460 --> 00:34:10,260
 kad je meni lijepo

522
00:34:10,260 --> 00:34:10,960
 i kad je sve ok.

523
00:34:10,960 --> 00:34:12,440
 Ili recimo kad me neko

524
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:13,240
 stvarno ponižava,

525
00:34:13,240 --> 00:34:14,560
 pogotovo osoba koju ja volim.

526
00:34:14,560 --> 00:34:16,240
 Dakle, kad me ponižava,

527
00:34:16,240 --> 00:34:18,180
 kad mi radi možda loše,

528
00:34:18,180 --> 00:34:19,740
 sad da li iz najbolje namere,

529
00:34:19,740 --> 00:34:20,820
 da li je ovako jednako nebitno.

530
00:34:20,820 --> 00:34:22,640
 Kad sam povrijeđena,

531
00:34:22,640 --> 00:34:24,260
 kad sam tužna i razočarana,

532
00:34:24,660 --> 00:34:26,300
 da li ja onda volim tu osobu?

533
00:34:26,300 --> 00:34:27,220
 Ili je to ono,

534
00:34:27,220 --> 00:34:29,060
 da je ono, ne znam,

535
00:34:29,060 --> 00:34:30,840
 želim da se da osoba od mene makne,

536
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:31,800
 to nije ljubav,

537
00:34:31,800 --> 00:34:32,700
 ona mene ne voli,

538
00:34:32,700 --> 00:34:33,460
 istog razloga ne voli,

539
00:34:33,460 --> 00:34:34,160
 neće mi, ono,

540
00:34:34,160 --> 00:34:36,100
 ta osoba ne zaslužuje

541
00:34:36,100 --> 00:34:37,360
 na neki način i moja osjeća i to.

542
00:34:37,360 --> 00:34:38,940
 E ne, znači tu se baš

543
00:34:38,940 --> 00:34:39,960
 ono pokazuje ljubav na dijelu.

544
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:41,500
 Znači da ti u tom trenutku

545
00:34:41,500 --> 00:34:42,440
 budeš dovoljno srpljiv,

546
00:34:42,440 --> 00:34:44,040
 dovoljno ponizan,

547
00:34:44,040 --> 00:34:45,660
 ne kažem sad da ćeš,

548
00:34:45,660 --> 00:34:47,120
 biti, ne znam,

549
00:34:47,120 --> 00:34:48,260
 po znaku navodnike,

550
00:34:48,260 --> 00:34:48,880
 jel budala.

551
00:34:48,880 --> 00:34:49,180
 Da.

552
00:34:49,180 --> 00:34:49,780
 Naravno,

553
00:34:49,780 --> 00:34:51,300
 ali na neki način

554
00:34:51,300 --> 00:34:52,300
 u svom srcu

555
00:34:52,300 --> 00:34:53,640
 zadrža taj dan mir.

556
00:34:53,640 --> 00:34:54,400
 Znači to je jedan

557
00:34:54,400 --> 00:34:55,960
 poštovanje prema toj osobi,

558
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:57,740
 razumijevanje prema toj osobi

559
00:34:57,740 --> 00:34:58,880
 i onako,

560
00:34:58,880 --> 00:34:59,800
 čvrsto

561
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:01,900
 odlučiti da

562
00:35:01,900 --> 00:35:03,500
 ta ljubav zapravo

563
00:35:03,500 --> 00:35:04,240
 pomaže

564
00:35:04,240 --> 00:35:05,460
 i toj osobi da se smiri,

565
00:35:05,460 --> 00:35:07,140
 i toj osobi da drugačije odreagira

566
00:35:07,140 --> 00:35:07,660
 i tako dalje.

567
00:35:07,660 --> 00:35:08,200
 Znači ono,

568
00:35:08,200 --> 00:35:09,540
 ljubav zapravo ne ovisi

569
00:35:09,540 --> 00:35:10,400
 o reakcijama drugih,

570
00:35:10,400 --> 00:35:11,860
 o ponašanju drugih prema tebe.

571
00:35:12,160 --> 00:35:13,000
 Ljubav je apsolutna.

572
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:14,840
 A pogotovo ljubav prema onima

573
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:15,800
 koji tebe možda i mrze,

574
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:17,120
 kojima smetaš,

575
00:35:17,120 --> 00:35:18,120
 koji te odbacuju.

576
00:35:18,120 --> 00:35:20,080
 Ej, ako voliš tog čovjeka,

577
00:35:20,080 --> 00:35:21,620
 ja sam to doživjela.

578
00:35:21,620 --> 00:35:22,720
 Znači to je milost

579
00:35:22,720 --> 00:35:23,300
 koja ono oslobađa.

580
00:35:23,300 --> 00:35:25,120
 Ko ćete li to moli vas podijeliti s nama?

581
00:35:25,120 --> 00:35:25,880
 Da, znači šta je,

582
00:35:25,880 --> 00:35:26,960
 to je ono nešto predivno.

583
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:27,880
 Dakle, ok,

584
00:35:27,880 --> 00:35:28,560
 ja nemam osobe

585
00:35:28,560 --> 00:35:29,700
 za koje ja znam da me mrze,

586
00:35:29,700 --> 00:35:30,800
 ali imam osobe

587
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:31,780
 za koje možda,

588
00:35:31,780 --> 00:35:34,080
 koji su možda manje dragi,

589
00:35:34,080 --> 00:35:36,100
 koje možda u nekom trenutku

590
00:35:42,160 --> 00:35:43,100
 bi da su dalje od mene,

591
00:35:43,100 --> 00:35:44,540
 da nismo u to.

592
00:35:44,540 --> 00:35:47,160
 A sad pomisl na tu osobu

593
00:35:47,160 --> 00:35:48,580
 jednostavno me ispunja radošću.

594
00:35:48,580 --> 00:35:50,340
 Baš ne moram ja tu osobu vidjeti,

595
00:35:50,340 --> 00:35:50,940
 ne moramo se družiti.

596
00:35:50,940 --> 00:35:52,520
 Ali onako iskreno je uvolim,

597
00:35:52,520 --> 00:35:53,600
 prihvaćam i želim je

598
00:35:53,600 --> 00:35:54,960
 stvarno od srca sve najbolje.

599
00:35:54,960 --> 00:35:56,200
 Čak neke osobe

600
00:35:56,200 --> 00:35:57,420
 koje su me nesjesno

601
00:35:57,420 --> 00:35:58,480
 jako, jako povrijedile,

602
00:35:58,480 --> 00:36:00,780
 možda ne,

603
00:36:00,780 --> 00:36:02,000
 ona ne misle da je to direktno,

604
00:36:02,000 --> 00:36:03,120
 ali nekako, naravno,

605
00:36:03,120 --> 00:36:04,240
 direktno se ticalo i mene

606
00:36:04,240 --> 00:36:05,040
 u nekim situacijama.

607
00:36:05,040 --> 00:36:06,580
 I ono, čovjek bi bio

608
00:36:06,580 --> 00:36:07,000
 i ne znam,

609
00:36:07,720 --> 00:36:09,160
 jako i ljut i ogoćen

610
00:36:09,160 --> 00:36:11,140
 i nekako htio bi toj osobi

611
00:36:11,140 --> 00:36:11,800
 možda i lošo

612
00:36:11,800 --> 00:36:12,940
 i da je se vrati

613
00:36:12,940 --> 00:36:14,840
 sve to skupa što je ona vama napravila.

614
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:16,400
 Ja za sve te osobe

615
00:36:16,400 --> 00:36:17,960
 osjećam toliko ljubav

616
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:19,680
 i da, evo, iskreno ono,

617
00:36:19,680 --> 00:36:21,000
 dala bih im sve na svijetu.

618
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:22,140
 Baš bih iskreno godila

619
00:36:22,140 --> 00:36:22,980
 da se i oni spase,

620
00:36:22,980 --> 00:36:23,640
 da se promjene.

621
00:36:23,640 --> 00:36:24,880
 I to je ono baš ono

622
00:36:24,880 --> 00:36:26,560
 zbilja divno i oslobađajuće.

623
00:36:26,560 --> 00:36:29,780
 Koliko deset ciklusa

624
00:36:29,780 --> 00:36:31,000
 kemoterapije ste prošli,

625
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:31,360
 je li tako?

626
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:32,520
 I jesam na početku

627
00:36:32,520 --> 00:36:33,400
 svoje bolesti.

628
00:36:34,200 --> 00:36:37,440
 Da, pa je ovako.

629
00:36:37,440 --> 00:36:38,880
 Znači, u kratko,

630
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:41,160
 dakle, kad je prije dvije i pol godine,

631
00:36:41,160 --> 00:36:43,600
 znači, kad je krenula moja terapija,

632
00:36:43,600 --> 00:36:45,900
 ja sam počela, dakle,

633
00:36:45,900 --> 00:36:47,620
 kemoterapije su krenule

634
00:36:47,620 --> 00:36:48,880
 i pametni ljekovi i ostalo,

635
00:36:48,880 --> 00:36:49,860
 dok se nije,

636
00:36:49,860 --> 00:36:51,960
 i to je, dakle, odrađeno

637
00:36:51,960 --> 00:36:53,520
 i nastavio se s pametnim ljekom

638
00:36:53,520 --> 00:36:54,900
 još godinu i pol i tako,

639
00:36:54,900 --> 00:36:56,160
 dok se nije ustanovilo

640
00:36:56,160 --> 00:36:57,660
 da zapravo je on krivu diagnozu.

641
00:36:57,660 --> 00:37:00,660
 Da, to je sad priča za sebe.

642
00:37:00,660 --> 00:37:04,160
 Uglavnom, evo, desila se nekakav propust

643
00:37:04,160 --> 00:37:04,860
 što možemo.

644
00:37:04,860 --> 00:37:06,260
 Uglavnom,

645
00:37:06,260 --> 00:37:07,840
 ispostavljeno je da sam ja

646
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:09,960
 sve te ljekove primala,

647
00:37:09,960 --> 00:37:11,380
 zapravo, ne možemo reći,

648
00:37:11,380 --> 00:37:11,860
 bez veze,

649
00:37:11,860 --> 00:37:13,900
 ali, ono, nepotrebno.

650
00:37:13,900 --> 00:37:16,060
 I, vjerojatno, su i ti ljekovi

651
00:37:16,060 --> 00:37:17,400
 napravili svoje u mom organizmu,

652
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:18,280
 tako da, kad se krenula

653
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:19,140
 s pravom terapijom,

654
00:37:19,140 --> 00:37:21,460
 onda ona baš nije odragirala

655
00:37:21,460 --> 00:37:22,180
 kako je trebala,

656
00:37:22,180 --> 00:37:23,140
 jer i moj organizam bio,

657
00:37:23,140 --> 00:37:24,480
 eto, u tom trenutku, možda...

658
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:26,480
 Čekajte, krivu diagnozu tumora ili...

659
00:37:26,480 --> 00:37:27,560
 Da, da, da, vrste tumora.

660
00:37:27,560 --> 00:37:27,880
 Vrste tumora.

661
00:37:27,880 --> 00:37:28,600
 Vrste tumora, da.

662
00:37:34,160 --> 00:37:35,380
 Užu da, ipak, riječ o drugom,

663
00:37:35,380 --> 00:37:36,660
 koji se i drugačije,

664
00:37:36,660 --> 00:37:37,400
 naravno, lječi,

665
00:37:37,400 --> 00:37:38,780
 i drugačije su linije lječenja,

666
00:37:38,780 --> 00:37:39,120
 i tako.

667
00:37:39,120 --> 00:37:40,180
 I, uglavnom, no,

668
00:37:40,180 --> 00:37:41,140
 prošla sam, dakle,

669
00:37:41,140 --> 00:37:42,780
 i taj protokol,

670
00:37:42,780 --> 00:37:46,060
 onda, nakon toga je vrlo brzo

671
00:37:46,060 --> 00:37:47,480
 prestao on djelovat,

672
00:37:47,480 --> 00:37:48,240
 pa smo išli na treći,

673
00:37:48,240 --> 00:37:48,900
 četvrti, blablabla.

674
00:37:48,900 --> 00:37:49,840
 Uglavnom se istrošilo,

675
00:37:49,840 --> 00:37:51,280
 ovaj, dosta toga,

676
00:37:51,280 --> 00:37:52,540
 i, ovaj,

677
00:37:52,540 --> 00:37:54,020
 predzadnja terapija je bila

678
00:37:54,020 --> 00:37:55,060
 jako, ono, dobra,

679
00:37:55,060 --> 00:37:56,080
 lijepo se mu podnosila,

680
00:37:56,780 --> 00:37:58,600
 i sve, sve to bilo ovo i dobro.

681
00:37:58,600 --> 00:37:59,140
 I, nekako,

682
00:37:59,140 --> 00:38:00,920
 ovoga ljeta sam primijentila

683
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:01,500
 da, da,

684
00:38:01,500 --> 00:38:02,940
 imam određene te gobe.

685
00:38:02,940 --> 00:38:04,680
 Znači, krenuli su opet volovi,

686
00:38:04,680 --> 00:38:06,760
 krenula je ta nekada zaduha.

687
00:38:06,760 --> 00:38:10,460
 Baš onako, život mi je bio dosta otežan

688
00:38:10,460 --> 00:38:12,400
 i primijentila sam baš razliku od prije.

689
00:38:12,400 --> 00:38:13,360
 Znači, nešto se dešava.

690
00:38:13,360 --> 00:38:15,680
 I već po iskusu sam znala

691
00:38:15,680 --> 00:38:16,240
 da, očigledno,

692
00:38:16,240 --> 00:38:17,940
 i ova terapija je prestala držati

693
00:38:17,940 --> 00:38:18,900
 po znakove navodnike.

694
00:38:18,900 --> 00:38:20,540
 I, ove,

695
00:38:20,540 --> 00:38:21,840
 no, dobro, evo, nisam znala

696
00:38:21,840 --> 00:38:22,580
 u kom, ono,

697
00:38:22,680 --> 00:38:23,720
 u kom sam fazi,

698
00:38:23,720 --> 00:38:24,400
 u kom sam smjeru,

699
00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:25,560
 što se dešava svojom bolešću.

700
00:38:25,560 --> 00:38:26,960
 Vjerojatno je progresija,

701
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:27,860
 ali nisam znala, ono,

702
00:38:27,860 --> 00:38:28,780
 do koje, do koje mjere.

703
00:38:28,780 --> 00:38:30,820
 Nakon ljeta,

704
00:38:30,820 --> 00:38:31,600
 kad sam došla u Zagreb,

705
00:38:31,600 --> 00:38:32,440
 onda su krenule sve moguće

706
00:38:32,440 --> 00:38:33,340
 pretrage, kontrole.

707
00:38:33,340 --> 00:38:35,560
 Ono, moja lječnica se jako,

708
00:38:35,560 --> 00:38:36,240
 jako, ovaj,

709
00:38:36,240 --> 00:38:37,360
 angažirala, naravno,

710
00:38:37,360 --> 00:38:38,860
 jer, ono,

711
00:38:38,860 --> 00:38:40,100
 htjeli smo znati zapravo

712
00:38:40,100 --> 00:38:41,920
 koliko je, koliko je ozbiljno,

713
00:38:41,920 --> 00:38:42,600
 koliko je opasno.

714
00:38:42,600 --> 00:38:44,620
 I ispala na kraju da je,

715
00:38:44,620 --> 00:38:45,100
 ono,

716
00:38:45,360 --> 00:38:46,580
 situacija poprlično,

717
00:38:46,580 --> 00:38:46,960
 ovaj,

718
00:38:46,960 --> 00:38:47,460
 ozbiljna,

719
00:38:47,460 --> 00:38:48,880
 s obzirom da je,

720
00:38:48,880 --> 00:38:50,400
 ja ne bih sad voljela

721
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:51,780
 zabrenuti naše gledatelje,

722
00:38:51,780 --> 00:38:52,220
 stvarno,

723
00:38:52,220 --> 00:38:52,640
 jer, ono,

724
00:38:52,640 --> 00:38:55,860
 unaprijed zapravo upozoravam

725
00:38:55,860 --> 00:38:57,000
 da sve što sad govorim

726
00:38:57,000 --> 00:38:57,740
 su isključivo

727
00:38:57,740 --> 00:38:58,760
 medicinske činjenice,

728
00:38:58,760 --> 00:38:59,620
 na koje se ja

729
00:38:59,620 --> 00:39:00,840
 čisto, onako,

730
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:01,640
 sporadično,

731
00:39:01,640 --> 00:39:02,240
 ovaj,

732
00:39:02,240 --> 00:39:02,940
 oslanjam.

733
00:39:02,940 --> 00:39:04,340
 Dakle, ja ih čujem,

734
00:39:04,340 --> 00:39:05,140
 ja ih uvažavam,

735
00:39:05,140 --> 00:39:06,320
 ja sam njih svjesna,

736
00:39:06,320 --> 00:39:07,560
 ja ću, naravno,

737
00:39:07,560 --> 00:39:09,220
 spremna sam na sve moguće

738
00:39:09,220 --> 00:39:10,640
 tretmane koje mi predlože,

739
00:39:11,100 --> 00:39:12,040
 ne odbijam ih,

740
00:39:12,040 --> 00:39:12,980
 ali,

741
00:39:12,980 --> 00:39:13,620
 to je to.

742
00:39:13,620 --> 00:39:14,400
 Znači,

743
00:39:14,400 --> 00:39:15,960
 to je, ono,

744
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:17,120
 kraj mog doticaja,

745
00:39:17,120 --> 00:39:17,640
 dakle, sa,

746
00:39:17,640 --> 00:39:18,400
 sa, ovaj,

747
00:39:18,400 --> 00:39:19,060
 realnošću,

748
00:39:19,060 --> 00:39:20,360
 a drugo je,

749
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:20,920
 mislim,

750
00:39:20,920 --> 00:39:21,400
 realnošću,

751
00:39:21,400 --> 00:39:23,180
 sa ovozemanjskim nekakvim činjenicama

752
00:39:23,180 --> 00:39:24,600
 ili medicinskim ograničavajućim,

753
00:39:24,600 --> 00:39:26,460
 a ono što zapravo

754
00:39:26,460 --> 00:39:28,160
 mene u svem u tome drži

755
00:39:28,160 --> 00:39:29,440
 i hrani i vodi

756
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:30,100
 i motivira,

757
00:39:30,100 --> 00:39:31,620
 a to je onaj pogled prema gore,

758
00:39:31,620 --> 00:39:33,160
 koji mi cijelo ono ne govori

759
00:39:33,160 --> 00:39:33,500
 da te,

760
00:39:33,500 --> 00:39:34,600
 kad si na dnu,

761
00:39:34,600 --> 00:39:36,760
 znači, kad dotakneš samo dno,

762
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:38,400
 tad je moje vrijeme.

763
00:39:38,400 --> 00:39:38,740
 Znači,

764
00:39:38,740 --> 00:39:39,760
 tad te ja podižem,

765
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:41,600
 tad ja činim svoja čudesa

766
00:39:41,600 --> 00:39:42,480
 i tad se ja proslavljam.

767
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:43,640
 I to je stvarno,

768
00:39:43,640 --> 00:39:44,420
 uistino tako.

769
00:39:44,420 --> 00:39:45,480
 Tako da, evo,

770
00:39:45,480 --> 00:39:47,220
